        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Withdrawal of Consent:</strong> You may withdraw consent for
          processing of your personal data at any time.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Grievance Redressal:</strong> You may file a complaint with our
          Grievance Officer if you believe your data has been mishandled.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <a
